insert into "products" ("body_html", "created_at", "handle", "id", "image", "images", "options", "product_type", "published_at", "published_scope", "tags", "template_suffix", "title", "metafields_global_title_tag", "metafields_global_description_tag", "updated_at", "variants", "vendor") values ('When the sun has set and the fires out, you can keep the fun going after its dark with a Coleman Tenaya Lake Lighted Fast Pitch 8-Person Cabin with Closet. Its built-in LED lighting system uses a fabric cover to provide soft, overhead illumination that you can adjust to a great level for reading a book or studying a map for the next days hike. With the built-in closet, you can bring all the luxuries from home and store them safely out of the elements without taking up precious tent space. Shelves and a hanger bar in the closet also make it easy to keep your clothes and gear organized, so you can skip digging though a pack for what you need. The Fast Pitch system uses pre-attached, color-coded top poles and hub, fast fit feet and snag-free Insta-Clip suspension to let you set up your tent 55 percent faster than a comparable Coleman tent with conventional setup. If it rains, this tent Keeps You Dry…Guaranteed, thanks to the WeatherTec system, which uses a tub floor with patented corner welds, protected seams, and a covered zipper to help keep water out. Meanwhile, the strong frame is tested to withstand 35+ MPH winds. A hinged door makes for easy comings and goings. Illumiline reflective guy lines are more visible at night so you dont get tripped up if you need to take a walk in the dark. Inside, theres enough room to stretch out on two queen-sized airbeds, and storage pockets help to keep small items organized. When its time to head home, the tent fits into an included wheeled carry bag for easy storage and transport.Coleman Tenaya Lake Lighted 8 Person Cabin Tent - Teal/Gray

Condition : This item is brand new, unopened and sealed in its original factory box.
